---
title: "_onAuctionEnd (BaseAuction + GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_aggregator: hasFeeAggregator?
    q_check_aggregator --> q_check_asset_bal: hasFeeAggregator == true
    q_check_aggregator --> q_check_out_bal: hasFeeAggregator == false
    q_check_asset_bal --> q_return_asset: assetBalance > 0
    q_return_asset --> q_check_out_bal: safeTransfer(asset, feeAggregator, balance)
    q_check_asset_bal --> q_check_out_bal: assetBalance == 0
    q_check_out_bal --> q_send_out: assetOutBalance > 0
    q_send_out --> q_revoke: safeTransfer(assetOut, assetOutReceiver, balance)
    q_check_out_bal --> q_revoke: assetOutBalance == 0
    q_revoke --> [*]: forceApprove(gpV2VaultRelayer, 0)

    note right of q_return_asset
        INV-001: Unsold assets return to feeAggregator when auction ends
        INV-002: Collected assetOut is sent to the designated receiver
        INV-003: GPV2 vault relayer approval is revoked on auction end
    end note
